high_descs: Turn around and face the yellow bed.
Pick up the red rag from the bed.
Turn to the table next to the bed.
Put the rag in the plate on the table.
Pick up the plate with the rag from the table.
Turn right to exit the room and take a left turn to reach the brown shelf.
Put the plate with the rag in the second shelf from bottom next to the salt shaker.
anns.task_desc: Put the plate with the rag in the shelf.

high_descs: Turn around to walk towards and face the bed.
Pick up the red towel from the bed.
Turn to the right to face the table in the corner.
Place the red towel on the gray dish on the table.
Pick up the gray dish on the table.
Turn to the right to exit the room then walk towards the shelf.
Place the gray plate on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place the red towel on the gray plate onto the bookshelf.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the bed to your right. Turn right.
Pick up the rag that is in the bed.
Turn around and walk to your right, when the chair is in your left, turn to your left and walt to the shelf.
Put the rag on the plate.
Pick up the plate with rag on it.
Turn around and walk to the wall, then turn left and go to the corridor. Turn around and go the shelf.
Put the plate in the second level of the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Take a plate with a rag to a shelf.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the bed.
Take the red cloth from the bed.
Turn around and go near the plate.
Put the cloth on the plate.
Take the plate with cloth from the table.
Turn around and go near the shelf.
Put the plate on the shelf with cloth on the rack.
anns.task_desc: Placed the cloth on the plate on the shelf.

high_descs: Turn around in the bed.
Take the red cloth from the bed.
Move around and move towards the plate on the table.
Place the cloth on the plate.
Take the plate along with the red cloth.
Turn around , head through the door and turn left towards the steel shelf.
Place the plate on the shelf with the cloth.
anns.task_desc: Move the cloth with plate from the bedroom to the shelf
